{"tid":1554083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果將來你被捕，一定要講自己同其他人一齊住","createTime":"2019-09-08T23:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T00:05:45.000Z","uid":271270,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"476019d4a5a01d1d84d129c880572e135a49fd47","tid":1554083,"uid":271270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:53:02.000Z","msg":"當然常識係律師未嚟之前係「我冇嘢講」，<br />\n但我地都知道黑警係公安，會千方百計唔俾你見律師。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果真係抵唔住威逼利誘嚴刑拷打要作供</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住無論你係咪一個人住都好，你都一定要話同其他人同住，有人會知道你失咗蹤，咁黑警先唔敢打死你然後做到你跳樓自殺！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b19bbf80244827a59d490c658a004d28b1678ad2","tid":1554083,"uid":271270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T23:54:14.000Z","msg":"一定要話自己同其他人一齊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b3ccbb10c352751ffb0911e62ff1b831fbefcc2","tid":1554083,"uid":134002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:05:45.000Z","msg":"會唔會搞到其他人都被失蹤<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}